CI/CD
=====

Create a CI/CD process on the GitLab server. Using Docker for the same will be a plus. 
The project will have Node as API server and Angular as a frontend with MySQL DB attached to nodejs. 
It should be implemented on a Linux ubuntu server. 
Create any test server. and share the credentials of the same with the access of GitLab as well. 
The server should point to any XYZ dummy domain to test the changes on successful CI/CD.

Nginx
=====
Setup a POC for Nginx reverse proxy where a request would hit the nginx server and it should be load balanced between 2 backend servers.
 

MySQL Replication
=================

Setup a POC for MySQL master-master replication.